Package: realestatebr
Type: Package
Title: Import Brazilian Real Estate Data into R
Version: 0.6.0
Authors@R: person(
    given = "Vinicius Oike",
    family = "Reginatto",
    email = "viniciusoike@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
Description: Provides functions to import Brazilian real estate data
    from various sources including BCB, FGV, ABECIP, ABRAINC, SECOVI, and BIS.
    Data is returned in tidy format.
